/Users/nioliu/projects/wsutil-go/example/group/chat_server.go
func main() {
	engine := gin.New()
	c := context.Background()
	// init root group
	g = group.NewGroupWithContext(c, ws.NewWrappedGorillaUpgrader(), group.WithMaxConnCnt(10))
 
	engine.Handle("GET", "/add", addUserToGroup)
 
	engine.Handle("POST", "/msg", func(c *gin.Context) {
		msg := c.Query("msg")
		log.Println(msg)
		if err := g.Broadcast(c, ws.Msg{
			Msg:     []byte(msg),
			MsgType: websocket.TextMessage,
		}); err != nil {
			log.Println(err)
			return
		}
	})
	if err := engine.Run("0.0.0.0:9090"); err != nil {
		log.Fatal(err)
	}
}
